    <!-- TOWRdocs Header
         Polar product parameters definition file.
    -->
   <!-- TOWRdocs Description
         Defines parameters to enable ingest of AMSR2, GPM Imagery, and ATMS products. The abbreviation and units
         need to match that of the input netcdf file.  This file has been edited from the baseline file of the same name.
         The defintion of wind speed, WS, used by SAR and AMSR2, is defined in the baseline file parameters.xml
		 Although this file contains AMSR2 in the name, products from both AMSR2 and other instruments are defined.

		 9 Sep 2016 Added add'l MIRS ATMS parameters SIce, SWE, TSkin.
		 24 Sep 2016 updates to names of GMI imagery.
		 
     -->
    <!-- TOWRdocs Status
         Update this file as needed for use of the pointset plugin in 16.4.1 and beyond.  This file is a modification to the
         base file of the same name to add new parameters. Check parameters.xml and any other parameter definition files in this
         or base-level directories for redundancies before adding to this file.
         Redefine ATMS rain rate as Rain_Rate to avoid potential conflict with radar refl (RR) in baseline
         Contributors: SPoRT EPDT members (Dec 1-3 2015).
         10/7/2019 Added WSPD_QC
    -->
    <!-- TOWRdocs POC
         Lee Byerle 10/7/2019
   -->
